  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一张Kikwiflow的嵌入式架构图，核心是展示它如何与用户的Spring Boot应用集成。最左边应该是用户的应用层，包含业务代码和一个可选的REST API。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sua Aplicação (Spring Boot)",
        "UserCode",
        "KikwiRestApi"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，UserCode这里标注Controllers和Services对吧？KikwiRestApi是可选的管理API。这两个组件都要连到Kikwiflow平台内部吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserCode",
        "KikwiRestApi"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，都要连。中间这层是Kikwiflow嵌入式平台，里面用CQRS模式分成两个核心模块：CommandEngine和QueryService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Plataforma Kikwiflow (Embarcada)",
        "CommandEngine",
        "QueryService",
        "Orquestração e Consulta (CQRS)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了中间层，CQRS子图里放了CommandEngine和QueryService。接下来是扩展点部分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CommandEngine",
        "QueryService",
        "Orquestração e Consulta (CQRS)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，下面要有\"Pontos de Extensão\"，也就是安全逻辑层。包含Rules和Delegates两个扩展点，业务规则用DecisionRule，自动化任务用JavaDelegate。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pontos de Extensão (Lógica Segura)",
        "Rules",
        "Delegates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Rules和Delegates都是CommandEngine调用的对吧？QueryService不需要直接访问它们？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CommandEngine",
        "QueryService",
        "Rules",
        "Delegates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，只有CommandEngine会触发业务规则和自动化任务。QueryService只读数据，走另一条线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CommandEngine",
        "QueryService",
        "Rules",
        "Delegates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那最底层是数据层，我打算叫\"Camada de Dados (Pluggable)\"，里面放Persistence节点，支持InMemory、MongoDB等多种实现。这样命名可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Camada de Dados (Pluggable)",
        "Persistence"
