      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，Pluggable这个特性要突出。现在把连接关系理一下：UserCode和KikwiRestApi都要分别连到CommandEngine和QueryService。",
